      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      int getDelay()
      The minimum duration that must elapse between sending this packet and the original spawn packet - for most, this is 1 tick.

    • Method Detail

      • getIdentifier

        IEntityIdentifier getIdentifier()
        Get the identifier that this packet is acting on. This will be null for entity destroy packets
        Returns:
        the identifier of the entity being changed by this packet

      • getDelay

        int getDelay()
        The minimum duration that must elapse between sending this packet and the original spawn packet - for most, this is 1 tick.
        Returns:
        the number of ticks that should be waited in between sending the spawn packet and sending this packet.

      • getRawPacket

        com.comphenix.protocol.events.PacketContainer getRawPacket()
        Gets the raw ProtocolLib packet container that is used by the engine to send this packet to the client.
        Returns:
        the raw packet with modifications
